# Hardware used:
- ESP32 
- 2x 1meter pipe
- Box as a base
- Umbrella
- Showerhead and hose
- 3D-printed holder and cover for the showerhead
- Speaker + audio module with microSD card reader
- 2 Buttons
- Vibration motor + MOSFET
- 1meter LED strip
- 1 LED + resistor
- Breadboard + wires

# Connections:
Vibration motor to GPIO 2 via MOSFET
Showerhead LED to pin via resistor 23
Start shower button pin 13
Toggle country selection pin 12
LED strip DATA_PIN 27
LED strip CLOCK_PIN 14
DFPlayer RX_PIN 16
DFPlayer TX_PIN 17